[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michael Rhodes: South African flanker signs new Saracens contract

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Saracens flanker Michael Rhodes has signed a new deal with the Premiership and European Champions Cup winners.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 28-year-old South African will now remain at Allianz Park until the summer of 2019.
Rhodes featured 27 times for Sarries last season after joining from Super Rugby outfit Stormers.
"Michael has quickly become a key member of the team and he is entering his prime as a player," said director of rugby Mark McCall.
